high_descs: Turn to your left, walk forwards, and then walk to the white table on your left.
Pick up the head of lettuce from the white table.
Turn around and walk forwards, and then walk to the sink on your left.
Put the head of lettuce into the sink, turn on the water, then drain the water and take the lettuce out of the sink.
Turn back around and walk back to the white table on your right.
Set the head of lettuce down on the table next to the brown plate.
anns.task_desc: Wash off the head of lettuce from the white table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the white table with the toaster
Grab the lettuce off of the table
Turn around and go to the sink
Wash the lettuce in the sink and then take it out
Turn left and go straight to the white table with the toaster
Put the lettuce on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting clean lettuce on a white table

high_descs: Turn around then head to the table on your left
Pick up the cabbage on the table
Turn right then head to the sink
Put the cabbage in the sink and rinse it
Turn left then face the table
Put the cabbage on the table beside the plate
anns.task_desc: Put the clean cabbage on the table
